    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## HSL Fee Collections — Push to Google Sheets\n\n**Webhook URL** — After activating, copy the production webhook URL and set it as `SHEETS_PUSH_WEBHOOK_URL` in your Next.js `.env.local`.\n\n**How it works:**\n- Next.js sends `{ rows: [...] }` to this webhook\n- Each row is matched against the sheet by **CASE LINK** column\n- Matched rows are updated in place; unmatched rows are appended\n- Returns `{ pushed: N }` to Next.js",
        "height": 328,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 6
